    "It bridges feature disparities through a semantic interaction mechanism and captures long-range dependencies and local appearance details via a dual-branch structure.• BDG-Net [50] aggregates high-level features to generate a boundary distribution map, which is fed into a boundary distribution-guided decoder and employs a multi-scale feature interaction strategy to enhance segmentation precision.",
